      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m selling my favorite set of wheels, and it\u2019s been a total rockstar for me. It\u2019s in really solid condition and still looks great out on the road! It\u2019s super dependable and honestly just a blast to drive. I\u2019ve really looked after this car, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who\u2019ll appreciate it just as much. Drop me a message if you\u2019re interested\u2014I\u2019d love to chat!",
