    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and refined comfort. The exterior retains a brilliant gloss with its deep metallic finish, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car of this age and consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a strictly smoke-free environment featuring premium leather seating that remains supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, from the responsive touchscreen infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection; the brakes are sharp, and the high-performance tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car drives straight, shifts cleanly, and offers a reliable, sophisticated experience for its next owner. Includes two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
