      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and still runs like a dream. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why I\u2019ve enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 32500.0,
