    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear, responsive power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural and internal longevity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the balanced handling and tactile steering feedback synonymous with the E46 chassis. While showing honest signs of use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping remain crisp.",
